By Andile Mngxitama Looks like no one in parliament noticed that those who met the contemporary representative of the British Crown, Lord Robin Renwick, under the secrecy of the Chatham House Rule are accusing the African National Congress (ANC) of being a servant of the Crown. The hypocrisy is staggering! These Robin Renwick boys want to have monopoly over being sellouts. Andile Mngxitama is the President of Black First Land First (BLF), a radical black consciousness organization. Reading list: Who Is Lord Robin Renwick Julius Malema’s Handler From London? What Exactly Is Chatham House The Royal Institute Of International Affairs And Why Did It Host EFF President Julius Malema? ‘Renwick forced Malema to bow down to Ramaphosa’, says Mngxitama Did FNB Fund The EFF Trip To London? Also, Why Was Johann Rupert So Angry?